    <div class="well" id="vote-flipping-caught-tape" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0Q9NSVUu8nk">Vote Flipping Caught on Tape</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>The engineers who &#8220;designed&#8221; these machines, and the civil servants who approved their use, should be named, shamed and banned from ever being involved in electoral process again.  Love the way the guy is trying to argue &#8220;Well, this would only happen if the machine is misconfigured&#8221;, then configures it correctly and it STILL fucks up.</p>

