    <div class="well" id="how-nate-silver-went-forecasti" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://nymag.com/news/features/51170/">How Nate Silver Went From Forecasting Baseball Games to Forecasting Elections</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Great profile in New York Magazine of Nate Silver and the sterling work he&#8217;s been doing at fivethirtyeight.com. Got to love anyone who can make a living from a combination of baseball, politics and obsessive number-crunching.</p>

