    <div class="well" id="report-60-million-people-youd-" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.theonion.com/content/node/87385">Report: 60 Million People You&#39;d Never Talk To Voting For Other Guy | The Onion</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>The US political &#8220;system&#8221; in a nutshell: &#8220;According to an eye-opening report released Tuesday, 60 million people whom you would never talk to, would never be in a position to talk to, and wouldn&#8217;t even be able to talk to if you tried will be voting for the other candidate in this year&#8217;s presidential election, and there is nothing you can do about it.&#8221;</p>

